---
By: Han Shan
Source:
  ISBN: 1556591403
  Locus:
    Page: 239
  Publisher: Copper Canyon Press
  Title: The Collected Songs of Cold Mountain
  Translator: Red Pine
---
From a lofty mountain peak
the view extends forever
I sit here unknown
the lone moon lights Cold Spring
in the spring there is no moon
the moon is in the sky
I sing this one song
a song in which there is no Zen
